      <div align="center" style="padding:10px;"><span class="h_blue_13pt_left">United Nations Convention on Contracts for the International Sale of Goods</span><br />
			<span class="h_blue_13pt_normal">Vienna, 11 April 1980</span></div>
<div id="TabbedPanels1" class="TabbedPanels">
      	      <ul class="TabbedPanelsTabGroup">
          <li class="TabbedPanelsTab" tabindex="0">&nbsp;Introductory Note&nbsp;</li>
